  "MAIN_BODY": "<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;, sans-serif; color: #0070C0;\">第三届CCF芯片大会 CCF Chip 2026</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;, sans-serif; color: #0070C0;\">论文征集</strong></p><p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">CCF芯片大会是中国计算机和芯片领域专家阵容最强、报告内容最丰富、参会规模最大、覆盖芯片研制全周期的旗舰盛会。诚挚欢迎从事芯片领域的专家学者、工程技术人员以及在校学生踊跃投稿并参会！让我们共同见证盛会，推动芯片技术迈向新的高度！</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">征文范围（包括但不限于以下领域）</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;容错计算：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">容错计算与应用</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">集成电路和软件测试理论与技术</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">硬件安全、容错、可信等技术</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">新型计算及应用</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;计算机工程与工艺：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">计算机工程总体设计新方法</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">电路系统、</span>IC<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">器件设计</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">EDA<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">及</span>CAD/CAT<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">技术</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">电磁兼容性设计、抗恶劣环境与加固技术</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;计算机体系结构：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">处理器</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">加速器，微体系结构设计新方法</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">存储系统，缓存和内存优化，</span>I/O<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">设计优化</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">新型体系结构，面向新应用的体系结构支撑</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">并行与高性能计算，云和大数据系统</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">各类针对能耗、可靠性、可用性、可扩展性的优化</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">产业领域实际系统设计经验分享、新应用新架构探索</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;集成电路设计：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">系统设计、系统级建模和设计方法</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">寄存器传输级设计、逻辑</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">高层综合与优化</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">物理设计、嵌入式和信息物理系统</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">设计验证、可测试性设计、芯片敏捷开发</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">新器件、技术与应用</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">征文要求：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">本次会议接受中文或英文稿件，所有投稿论文将接受严格的学术评审。论文录取后需要作者自行注册会议、并到会作口头报告。本次会议将以电子论文集形式供会议交流（无版权）。投稿论文请用</span>word<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">或</span>pdf<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">，篇幅不限。建议中文或英文稿件使用</span>CCF Chip 2026<span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">大会提供模板（网页底部链接）。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">若投稿论文拟推荐至期刊，请根据期刊要求选择中文或英文，使用期刊模板，满足期刊篇幅要求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">论文推荐：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">1</span>）《电子与信息学报》会为本次大会投稿开通专门投稿渠</span><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">道，请想要推荐至该学报的论文直接登录《电子与信息学报》网站注册投稿，投稿时务必在作者留言一栏中注明：“先进集成电路技术专刊”，该渠道会加速审稿流程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pzkDlUKfRS6iqZlJ8KE4iQ\" style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pzkDlUKfRS6iqZlJ8KE4iQ</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">2</span>）其他论文通过以下链接投稿：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><a href=\"https://conf.ccf.org.cn/ccfchip2026/\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">https://conf.ccf.org.cn/ccfchip2026/</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">经大会程序委员审稿评分后，大会录用论文可推荐至以下学报，由学报编辑安排二次审稿后决定是否最终录用：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">l</span><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">《网络与信息安全学报》硬件安全专题征稿：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 80px;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_xBRkqbJANzUdVQX9-WE_Q\"><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_xBRkqbJANzUdVQX9-WE_Q</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">l</span><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">《计算机工程与科学》</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 80px;\"><a href=\"http://joces.nudt.edu.cn/\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">http://joces.nudt.edu.cn/</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">l</span><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\">《微电子学》</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 80px;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Dtn_FE3lzzI5U0HcZ8MCEQ\" target=\"_self\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Dtn_FE3lzzI5U0HcZ8MCEQ\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Dtn_FE3lzzI5U0HcZ8MCEQ</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">l</span><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">Integrate Circuits and Systems (ICAS)</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 80px;\"><a href=\"https://www.qk.sjtu.edu.cn/ics/EN/home\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">https://www.qk.sjtu.edu.cn/ics/EN/home</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Chip</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 80px;\"><a href=\"https://www.qk.sjtu.edu.cn/chip/EN/home\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;;\">https://www.qk.sjtu.edu.cn/chip/EN/home</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 32px; margin-top: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋_GB2312; color: rgb(241, 90, 41); text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">3）录用的优秀英文论文将被推荐至：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 56px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 78, 161); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\">• ACM TODAES special issue</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-family: Aptos; text-indent: 80px;\"><a href=\"https://dl.acm.org/journal/todaes\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman Regular&quot;; text-decoration: none;\">https://dl.acm.org/journal/t